00:16:41,660 --> 00:16:46,580
♪Into a spiral of thoughts,
memories rewinding♪

288
00:16:46,580 --> 00:16:50,380
♪Feelings both strange and familiar♪

289
00:16:50,380 --> 00:16:55,180
♪I just know you're
where my heart belongs♪

290
00:16:55,180 --> 00:16:58,020
♪Can't remember
when this flutter started♪

291
00:16:58,020 --> 00:17:00,700
♪Or how it's supposed to end♪

292
00:17:01,060 --> 00:17:06,620
♪Goodbye to the world rushing in♪

293
00:17:07,020 --> 00:17:13,820
♪Let me hide in your eyes
and never leave♪

294
00:17:14,100 --> 00:17:18,780
♪Feel the rhythm of your heartbeat♪

295
00:17:18,940 --> 00:17:25,740
♪Every tomorrow seems worth the wait♪

296
00:17:26,060 --> 00:17:32,860
♪Let me fill the emptiness of a century♪

297
00:17:33,060 --> 00:17:37,540
♪As the wind brushes past your hem♪

298
00:17:37,540 --> 00:17:40,900
♪All my hidden feelings come undone♪

299
00:17:40,900 --> 00:17:47,820
♪Right as I confess my love♪
